<collectingCountry box="[285,366,1799,1824]" name="Turkey" pageId="16" pageNumber="455">Turkey</collectingCountry>
, up to 
<quantity box="[440,534,1800,1824]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.4" pageId="16" pageNumber="455" unit="m" value="2400.0">2,400 m</quantity>
, and at eastern Mediterranean localities, on the mountains near Mugla (
